{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/AboutQuerent.gif?t=1736257060\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Querent is a truly unique tactical role playing game. Explore an alternate Southwest America as an exile of the government to uncover a dark force possessing local animals. Recruit and unite the locals to utilize their unique hypnotic skills. Free the animals under the mesmerism of something deep below the town of Sunset Junction.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/HeaderText.png?t=1736257060\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/Full_Character_Customization.png?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize the appearance and body type of your exile. Build your deck as you play to decide what kind of person you will become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/CharacterCustomization.gif?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/Six_Skill_Sets.png?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your skill deck from  6 suits. Will you use true grit, harness the power of nature, or energize your party with your natural wit? The combinations are endless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/AbilitySelect.gif?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/26_Unique_Abilities.png?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock mesmeric abilities you can use to free animals or break through barriers to your path.\u00a0Build a deck for each character in a fast paced turn based battle system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/Combat.gif?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/8_Playable_Characters.png?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit a diverse group of your fellow exiles and unlock their hidden abilities. Build your relationships to unite the exiles against a dark force living beneath your feet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/charactersPreview.png?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/Solve_Puzzles_Your_Way.png?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No obstacle has only one solution. Use different skills or party members to overcome any challenge that awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1736257060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736257060","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/page.bg.jpg?t=1736257060","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369500/6038b328e865ca6a014d2f49bfd183ebaaeac